  "text": "A team is defined as a work arrangement in which individuals work interdependently to achieve goals that are collectively responsible for the results of work, where a group and individuals are seen as whole social identities [CITATION_1] . This condition makes it easier for team members to utilize their knowledge and increase the creation of new knowledge [CITATION_2] . Furthermore, teamwork can also benefit individual creativity, because individuals tend to experience positive feelings through working together on teams [CITATION_3] ).",
